ast.source:
Opens a prompt that asks for an input.
Returns a string with the input.
You need to await the result of inputPrompt.
Editor buttons are text editing buttons like delete, enter, allcaps - these are only displayed if lines is greater than 1 
Custom components are components that you can add to the prompt. These will be displayed between the text input area and the buttons.
blockPointerInputOutsideModal will block pointer input outside the modal. This is useful if you want to prevent the user accidently closing the modal or interacting with the excalidraw canvas while the prompt is open.
controlsOnTop when set to true will move all the buttons to the top of the modal, leaving the text area at the bottom. This feature was developed for Scribble Helper script to avoid your palm pressing buttons while scribbling.
buttons.action(input: string) => string
The button action function will receive the actual input string. If action returns null, input will be unchanged. If action returns a string, input will receive that value when the promise is resolved. iconId is the lucide.dev icon name. If iconId is provided caption will be ignored, simply submit "" as caption in that case. 
example:
<code>let fileType = '';
const filename = await utils.inputPrompt (
  'Filename',
  '',
  '',
,  [
    {
      caption: 'Markdown',
      action: ()=>{fileType='md';return;}
    },
    {
      caption: 'Excalidraw',
      action: ()=>{fileType='ex';return;}
    }
  ]
);</code>

ast.target:
打开一个提示输入框。
返回包含输入的字符串。
您需要等待inputPrompt的结果。
编辑器按钮是文本编辑按钮，如删除、回车、全大写——这些仅在lines大于1时显示。
自定义组件是您可以添加到提示中的组件。这些将显示在文本输入区域和按钮之间。
blockPointerInputOutsideModal将阻止模态框外的指针输入。如果您想防止用户意外关闭模态框或在提示打开时与excalidraw画布交互，这很有用。
controlsOnTop设置为true时，将所有按钮移动到模态框顶部，将文本区域留在底部。此功能是为Scribble Helper脚本开发的，以避免在涂鸦时手掌按压按钮。
buttons.action(input: string) => string
按钮动作函数将接收实际的输入字符串。如果action返回null，输入将保持不变。如果action返回字符串，则当promise解析时输入将接收该值。iconId是lucide.dev图标名称。如果提供了iconId，将忽略caption，只需在该情况下提交""作为caption。
示例：
<code>let fileType = '';
const filename = await utils.inputPrompt (
  'Filename',
  '',
  '',
,  [
    {
      caption: 'Markdown',
      action: ()=>{fileType='md';return;}
    },
    {
      caption: 'Excalidraw',
      action: ()=>{fileType='ex';return;}
    }
  ]
);</code>
